data.description: Introducing this charming home nestled in the sought-after Golden Hills neighborhood. This spacious family home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Located close to town, it provides easy access to amenities such as stores, restaurants, and parks while also embracing the calmness of the Tehachapi mountains.This three-bedroom, two-bath property sits on a generous .41-acre lot, providing ample space for all your needs. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by gorgeous dark wood floors and a beautiful bright, white updated kitchen. The open floorpan opens up to a modern white brick fireplace for those cozy winter nights. The home also has a dedicated separate laundry room, making household chores a breeze and keeping your living space clutter free. This home is designed for a family's dream lifestyle, featuring not one, but two living rooms, which can easily be transformed into an extra room, a game room or a playful haven for a kids playroom. The possibilities are endless!For those with a green thumb, the property includes several garden beds, perfect for cultivating your favorite blooms and herbs, fruit trees, and a small greenhouse to extend your gardening season. In addition to these wonderful features, this property also includes an unfinished chicken coop!Don't miss the opportunity to make 20300 Mini Court your new haven in beautiful Tehachapi. It's the ideal blend of space, comfort, and endless possibilities, waiting for you to call it home.
